                     <interp inst="t18210606-84-person1011" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am an officer; the prisoner was given in my charge; I only found a few halfpence on him.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I have been at sea ten years, and was very hungry and distressed.</p>
